curam.common.util.xml.dom

Class ProcessingInstruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Content
      • curam.common.util.xml.dom.ProcessingInstruction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomWrapper

    public class ProcessingInstruction
extends Content
    A ProcessingInstruction (PI) allows documents to contain instructions for applications. This implementation wraps a dom4j ProcessingInstruction.
